com.analog.lyric.options

Class DoubleRangeOptionKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.analog.lyric.options.OptionKey<OptionDoubleList>
      • com.analog.lyric.options.DoubleListOptionKey
        • com.analog.lyric.options.DoubleRangeOptionKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IOptionKey<OptionDoubleList>, java.io.Serializable

    public class DoubleRangeOptionKey
extends DoubleListOptionKey
    Key for options holding a pair of double values that define a range.

    This requires that the values have exactly two elements and that the second is greater than or equal to the first.

    Since:
    0.07
